01:40:29.652 --> 01:40:31.904
One day the boy came to me
with a clipping.

01:40:31.946 --> 01:40:36.158
"This is my destiny.
This is my birthright. "

01:40:36.241 --> 01:40:38.535
It was a story about the pistol...

01:40:38.535 --> 01:40:41.830
how they found it
in the mines, stashed away.

01:40:41.955 --> 01:40:44.833
When I asked why
it meant so much to him,

01:40:44.916 --> 01:40:47.585
