01:41:58.150 --> 01:42:01.903
'The nobleman's son took
the mighty weapon into his hands.

01:42:02.028 --> 01:42:03.988
'A perfect fit. '

01:42:09.494 --> 01:42:11.245
'It did not work.

01:42:12.913 --> 01:42:16.250
'The nobleman took it as a bad omen.

01:42:16.333 --> 01:42:19.419
