in unworthy hands.

01:42:21.880 --> 01:42:26.134
'The gunsmith urged him to try it
one last time, and so he did. '

01:42:28.594 --> 01:42:32.681
'The nobleman was insulted by the
ineptness, angry with the gunsmith.

01:42:33.724 --> 01:42:35.768
'They argued.

01:42:45.527 --> 01:42:50.198
