hear her heart break.

01:43:50.544 --> 01:43:54.757
'She fearlessly surrendered
her bitter spirit unto purgatory. '

01:43:57.593 --> 01:44:00.178
'The pistol contains
her damned soul. '

01:44:03.765 --> 01:44:07.644
